long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Teeto is designed to enhance web application security and development by scanning for and identifying endpoints, secrets, and parameters embedded within web applications.

üìù Teeto offers a range of functionalities:

‚ñ∏ Web Page Scanning: Automatically detects and lists endpoints, secrets, and parameters found in a web page.
‚ñ∏ Data Export: Provides options to download the found data or copy it to the clipboard for external use.
‚ñ∏ Interactive UI: Results are neatly displayed in the extension's user interface for easy review.
‚ñ∏ Cumulative Data Scanning: Allows repeated scans across different sessions, accumulating and updating data.
‚ñ∏ Tab-Specific Data Storage: Maintains separate data sets for each tab, ensuring domain-specific organization.
